init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Those who can tap into it are known as Drakon.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Drakon are the only ones who can stand against the alien invaders.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the Drakon have their own secrets and agendas.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And they are not the only ones with their eyes on this new power.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Their thirst to possess Earth's new magic threatens to reignite a war that could not only destroy humanity, but the Drakon themselves.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Drakon have begun to abduct humans, experimenting on them with genetic manipulation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They have also begun to implant the Drakon symbiotic control device known as a SoulStone into humans.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: With this implantation, the Drakon are able to control these humans and use them as spies in order to control mankind.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But both the good and the evil Drakon are hunted by their enemies, and must remain hidden in human society.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Guardians, and the evil Drakon are known as Rogues.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You have been raised among humans, but you possess a power that both the Rogues and Guardians will do anything to control-the ability to wield

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: How will you make your own choices in a world filled with war, and where a single misstep can cost everything?
